------------------------------------------------------------
1st

1. First open the git terminal.
2. Then using cd command , direct it to the desktop.
3. Then make a repository in Github account.
4. Write git init, then git clone <repository link> in the terminal.
5. A folder will be created.
6. add files in the folder.
7. in the git terminal, write git add .
8. then git commit -m "Success".
9. Then git push -u origin main.
10. The files have been pushed to github.



